<subSubSection id="8C8E6575FF856A3AFD1794A11CDFBF49" pageId="126" pageNumber="885" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="C42B36FEFF856A3AFD1794A11CDFBF49" blockId="126.[745,1339,690,1109]" lastBlockId="126.[128,1338,1114,3200]" pageId="126" pageNumber="885">
Genetic data placed 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF856A3AFBE094A11A8DB82B" authorityName="Leach" authorityYear="1821" box="[1052,1165,760,793]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Scotophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="126" pageNumber="885" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="kuhlii">S. kuhlii</taxonomicName>
sister to all other species of 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF856A3AFC3295461A5BB872" box="[974,1115,799,832]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Scotophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="126" pageNumber="885" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Scotophilus</taxonomicName>
and completely separate from the widespread Asiatic species, S. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF856A3AFC9E95371DB8B8BD" baseAuthorityName="Horsfield" baseAuthorityYear="1831" box="[866,952,878,911]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Scotophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="126" pageNumber="885" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="heathii">heathii</taxonomicName>
. Seven subspecies (
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF856A3AFB1995371B33B8BD" authorityName="Leach" authorityYear="1821" box="[1253,1331,878,911]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Scotophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="126" pageNumber="885" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="kuhlii">kuhlii</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF856A3AFD1095C31D65B885" authorityName="Handley" authorityYear="1960" box="[748,869,922,951]" class="Liliopsida" family="Poaceae" genus="Lasiurus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="126" pageNumber="885" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="castaneus">castaneus</taxonomicName>
, consobrinus, gairdneri, panayensis, solutatus, and temminckii) have been recognized, but some names have been moved back and forth between S. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF856A3AFB0C92551B3BBF1F" authorityName="Leach" authorityYear="1821" box="[1264,1339,1036,1069]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Scotophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="126" pageNumber="885" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="kuhlii">kuhlii</taxonomicName>
and S. 
<taxonomicName id="03944D7DFF856A3AFCB792651DA1BF67" baseAuthorityName="Horsfield" baseAuthorityYear="1831" box="[843,929,1084,1109]" class="Mammalia" family="Vespertilionidae" genus="Scotophilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Chiroptera" pageId="126" pageNumber="885" phylum="Chordata" rank="species" species="heathii">heathii</taxonomicName>
, and there 1s no well-defined distribution for any subspecies. Monotypic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
